1. *Kažem* ti da je to dobro. (I'm telling you it's good.)
2. Nisam ti *kažem* da to treba da uradiš. (I'm not telling you to do that.)
3. On mi je *kažem* da će doći. (He told me he was coming.)
4. *Kaže* mi da nema vremena. (He tells me there is no time.)
5. *Kažu* da će biti tužno. (They say it will be sad.)
6. *Kažu* nešto drugo. (They are saying something else.)